body:
@lllidan-yuandian if you have not figured out how to resolve it. Add 
`"//tensorflow/contrib/lite/kernels:builtin_ops"` to libtflite.so should work. That is, the rule should be 

```
cc_binary(
    name = "libtflite.so",
    deps = [
        ":framework",
        "//tensorflow/contrib/lite/kernels:builtin_ops",
    ],
    linkshared=1
)
```
